How to Use;
Install Dependencies:
Make sure you have Python and the requests library installed. Install requests if not already available:

Copy code : pip install requests
Enable Gmail Access:
For Gmail, enable "Allow less secure apps" or generate an App Password from your Google account for enhanced security.

Run the Script:
Save the code in a file (e.g., trading_alert.py) and run it:

Copy code : python trading_alert.py
Set Thresholds: Input your desired upper and lower thresholds when prompted.
